      <title>李嘉诚支持的和记医药以 6.08 亿美元出售旗下子公司股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/li-ka-shing-backed-hutchmed-sells-stake-in-unit-for-608-million</link>
